To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private AroonOscillator _aroon;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_aroon = AROON(symbol, upPeriod, downPeriod);

// In OnData()
if (_aroon.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "aroonup", _aroon.AroonUp.Current.Value);
    Plot("My Indicators", "aroondown", _aroon.AroonDown.Current.Value);
    Plot("My Indicators", "aroonoscillator", _aroon.Current.Value);
}
